The paper discusses training a deep Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) from scratch for visual aesthetic analysis in images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of deep learning techniques to improve accuracy suggests the paper may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The mention of incremental training set and dataset suggests the paper may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
